672
00:57:17,902 --> 00:57:20,169
( sniffles )

673
00:57:20,171 --> 00:57:22,738
I DON'T EVEN KNOW IF
I BELIEVE IT MYSELF, BUT...

674
00:57:23,773 --> 00:57:25,574
I KNOW I CAN'T
CONTROL IT.

675
00:57:29,078 --> 00:57:31,213
THE MIND'S A PRISON
OF YOUR OWN MAKING.

676
00:57:32,949 --> 00:57:35,150
FUNNY THING ABOUT
THAT LITTLE FELLA--

677
00:57:35,152 --> 00:57:38,954
SO SMALL TO BE CARRYING
ALL THAT WEIGHT BY HIMSELF.

678
00:57:38,956 --> 00:57:40,756
YEAH, BUT HE'S STILL
CARRYING IT.

679
00:57:42,459 --> 00:57:44,460
YOU LOVE YOUR WIFE, MICHAEL?

680
00:57:46,062 --> 00:57:47,963
SHOW HER.

681
00:57:54,571 --> 00:57:55,938
IT JUST AIN'T RIGHT.

682
00:57:57,574 --> 00:58:00,542
THE MAN'S BEEN THROUGH HELL
AND BACK WITH HIS WIFE.

683
00:58:01,811 --> 00:58:04,680
- HIS WIFE?
- I'D LISTEN TO HIM.

684
00:58:04,682 --> 00:58:06,181
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

685
00:58:07,817 --> 00:58:09,818
IT PROBABLY AIN'T
MY PLACE TO SAY.

686
00:58:09,820 --> 00:58:12,988
<i>THIS TOWN IS</i>
<i>FULL OF SECRETS.</i>

687
00:58:12,990 --> 00:58:14,890
<i>WE'RE ALL JUST</i>
<i>CREATURES OF HABIT.</i>

688
00:58:14,892 --> 00:58:17,259
<i>WE DON'T LOOK TO RIGHT</i>
<i>OUR WRONGS.  WE JUST--</i>

689
00:58:17,261 --> 00:58:19,495
<i>WE JUST LIVE WITH THEM.</i>

690
00:59:06,743 --> 00:59:10,245
HAVE YOU NOTICED ANY STRANGE
PATTERNS WITH YOUR WIFE?

691
00:59:10,247 --> 00:59:13,181
FITS?  BLACKOUTS?

692
00:59:13,183 --> 00:59:14,816
SELF-MUTILATIONS?

693
00:59:29,232 --> 00:59:32,200
<i>( door opens, shuts )</i>

694
00:59:35,305 --> 00:59:37,272
YOUR WIFE WROTE
THAT PHRASE...

695
00:59:37,274 --> 00:59:38,807
<i>20 YEARS AGO.</i>

696
00:59:43,279 --> 00:59:45,280
<i>SHE WAS</i>
<i>A PATIENT HERE.</i>

697
00:59:45,282 --> 00:59:46,815
I-I WAS JUST AN INTERN,

698
00:59:46,817 --> 00:59:48,684
BUT I'LL NEVER FORGET IT.

699
00:59:48,686 --> 00:59:52,688
WE BROUGHT HER IN
AND WE OBSERVED HER
VERY CLOSELY--

700
00:59:52,690 --> 00:59:54,890
<i>BLANCH RACHEL BANKS.</i>

701
00:59:54,892 --> 00:59:57,292
<i>( little girl laughing )</i>

702
01:00:01,064 --> 01:00:02,931
Mike:
<i>THIS IS BULLSHIT.</i>
<i>YOU'RE BOTH--</i>

703
01:00:02,933 --> 01:00:04,199
<i>YOU'RE BOTH FULL OF SHIT.</i>

704
01:00:04,201 --> 01:00:06,001
THE BOTH OF YOU,
YOU'RE FULL OF SHIT!

705
01:00:08,805 --> 01:00:10,973
WE GET SO TANGLED

706
01:00:10,975 --> 01:00:13,241
IN OUR REGRETS
OF THE PAST.

707
01:00:13,243 --> 01:00:16,678
WE THINK WE CAN
JUST BURY IT FOREVER,

708
01:00:16,680 --> 01:00:19,247
CREATE A NEW IDENTITY,
START OVER.

709
01:00:19,249 --> 01:00:21,683
BUT THE TRUTH...

710
01:00:22,919 --> 01:00:24,653
<i>WILL SURFACE.</i>

711
01:00:26,656 --> 01:00:30,258
- I DARE YOU
TO GO INSIDE, BETHY.
- MOM SAID NOT TO GO INSIDE.

712
01:00:30,260 --> 01:00:33,629
- YOU'RE SUCH A MAMA'S GIRL.
- NO, I'M NOT.

713
01:00:33,631 --> 01:00:34,963
I HATE YOU!

714
01:00:36,299 --> 01:00:38,700
BLANCH, BLANCH, NO!

715
01:00:53,182 --> 01:00:54,383
( slams )

716
01:00:59,255 --> 01:01:01,890
Where is
your sister-- Beth?

717
01:01:03,326 --> 01:01:05,727
- Am I my sister's keeper?
- ( static buzzes )

718
01:01:08,831 --> 01:01:11,299
Why are you angry?

719
01:01:11,301 --> 01:01:13,135
<i>If you do</i>
<i>what is right,</i>

720
01:01:13,137 --> 01:01:15,671
<i>will you not</i>
<i>be accepted?</i>

721
01:01:16,439 --> 01:01:19,241
- Where is your sister?
-  <i>( voice whispers )</i>

722
01:01:19,243 --> 01:01:22,044
Her blood cries out
to me from the ground.

723
01:01:22,046 --> 01:01:23,345
( screaming )

724
01:01:23,347 --> 01:01:26,081
No, leave me alone,
please!

725
01:01:27,350 --> 01:01:29,051
( shrieking )

726
01:01:36,025 --> 01:01:38,226
( screaming )

727
01:01:42,131 --> 01:01:44,900
Mike:
NO NO NO NO NO.

728
01:01:44,902 --> 01:01:47,235
RACHEL, RACHEL.

729
01:01:47,237 --> 01:01:49,805
<i>THIS CAN'T BE--</i>

730
01:01:49,807 --> 01:01:51,840
<i>THIS CAN'T BE HAPPENING.</i>

731
01:01:54,911 --> 01:01:56,078
IT'S AN ANAGRAM.

732
01:02:06,222 --> 01:02:08,123
"ASMODEUS."

733
01:02:08,125 --> 01:02:09,925
Shaw:
<i>FROM THE BOOK OF ENOCH.</i>

734
01:02:09,927 --> 01:02:12,427
IT'S A HEBREW WORD
WHICH MEANS "TO DESTROY."

735
01:02:15,098 --> 01:02:17,332
ASMODEUS IS REFERRED
TO AS ONE OF THE SEVEN

736
01:02:17,334 --> 01:02:19,201
PRINCES OF HELL.

737
01:02:19,203 --> 01:02:21,169
<i>A FALLEN ANGEL</i>

738
01:02:21,171 --> 01:02:24,172
<i>CAST DOWN TO THE EARTH</i>
<i>FROM THE WAR IN HEAVEN.</i>

739
01:02:24,174 --> 01:02:27,142
A-- A DEMON OF LUST,

740
01:02:27,144 --> 01:02:28,744
HATE AND JEALOUSY,

741
01:02:28,746 --> 01:02:32,814
RESPONSIBLE FOR TWISTING
MEN'S DESIRES.

742
01:02:36,486 --> 01:02:39,020
THE COPS NEVER FOUND
HER BODY.

743
01:02:39,022 --> 01:02:41,189
WHAT BODY?

744
01:02:41,191 --> 01:02:43,391
WHEN THE POLICE
DISCOVERED YOUR WIFE

745
01:02:43,393 --> 01:02:45,160
SHE WAS INSIDE
AN ABANDONED HOME,

746
01:02:45,162 --> 01:02:47,462
SHAKING UNCONTROLLABLY.

747
01:02:47,464 --> 01:02:50,132
<i>WE BROUGHT HER IN</i>
<i>AND WE OBSERVED HER</i>

748
01:02:50,134 --> 01:02:52,167
<i>VERY CAREFULLY.</i>

749
01:02:53,136 --> 01:02:55,403
SHE DIDN'T SPEAK

750
01:02:55,405 --> 01:02:56,972
FOR WEEKS.

751
01:02:56,974 --> 01:02:58,507
<i>AND WHEN SHE</i>
<i>FINALLY DID TALK,</i>

752
01:02:58,509 --> 01:03:01,343
<i>SHE SAID THAT</i>
<i>HER SISTER BETHY</i>

753
01:03:01,345 --> 01:03:04,412
HAD BEEN RAPED
AND KILLED.

754
01:03:06,449 --> 01:03:08,250
SHE WAS LYING.

755
01:03:14,290 --> 01:03:15,357
( slams )

756
01:03:21,097 --> 01:03:23,198
BLANCH, THIS ISN'T FUNNY.

757
01:03:28,504 --> 01:03:30,071
BLANCH!

758
01:03:49,358 --> 01:03:51,526
( shrieking )

759
01:03:56,265 --> 01:03:57,999
SHHH.

760
01:04:03,906 --> 01:04:06,975
( sobs )

761
01:04:36,505 --> 01:04:38,240
( screams )

762
01:04:38,242 --> 01:04:40,909
<i>( alarm ringing )</i>

763
01:04:57,260 --> 01:04:59,060
<i>( insects chirping,</i>
<i>owl hoots )</i>

764
01:05:02,598 --> 01:05:04,532
ARE-- ARE YOU
TELLING ME THAT MY WIFE

765
01:05:04,534 --> 01:05:08,270
- IS POSSESSED BY A--
- THE MIND IS A POWERFUL THING.

766
01:05:08,272 --> 01:05:10,305
SHE DID
EVERYTHING SHE COULD

767
01:05:10,307 --> 01:05:12,140
TO BLOCK IT OUT.

768
01:05:13,342 --> 01:05:15,076
( exhales )

769
01:05:34,130 --> 01:05:36,097
HENDRICKS!

770
01:05:50,479 --> 01:05:52,480
SON OF A BITCH.

771
01:06:01,390 --> 01:06:03,358
<i>( keys rattling )</i>

772
01:06:19,976 --> 01:06:21,643
MY GOD.
WHAT HAPPENED?

773
01:06:24,513 --> 01:06:27,182
<i>WE'RE ALL JUST CREATURES</i>
<i>OF HABIT.</i>

774
01:06:27,184 --> 01:06:29,651
<i>I-- I WANTED HER.</i>

775
01:06:29,653 --> 01:06:32,554
WE GRASP ONTO IT.

776
01:06:34,623 --> 01:06:37,392
CAPABLE OF

777
01:06:37,394 --> 01:06:39,227
ANYTHING.

778
01:06:39,229 --> 01:06:41,429
I COULDN'T STOP MYSELF.

779
01:06:43,632 --> 01:06:46,768
( screaming )
DON'T TOUCH ME!

780
01:06:46,770 --> 01:06:49,604
- NATHAN, NATHAN!
- ( fabric rips )

781
01:06:49,606 --> 01:06:51,406
PLEASE!
GET OFF ME!

782
01:06:53,175 --> 01:06:55,744
( gasping )
DON'T!

783
01:06:58,314 --> 01:07:01,016
I CAN'T LIVE WITH MYSELF
FOR WHAT I DID.

784
01:07:02,385 --> 01:07:04,319
I KILLED HER.

785
01:07:17,800 --> 01:07:20,201
<i>( insects chirping )</i>

786
01:07:34,784 --> 01:07:37,786
<i>( wind gusting )</i>

787
01:08:22,164 --> 01:08:23,798
HENDRICKS?

788
01:08:23,800 --> 01:08:25,467
HENDRICKS?

789
01:08:29,105 --> 01:08:31,406
<i>( music box playing )</i>

790
01:08:38,114 --> 01:08:39,180
<i>( music stops )</i>

791
01:09:00,803 --> 01:09:03,204
<i>( melody playing )</i>

792
01:09:32,434 --> 01:09:34,269
<i>"MARTHA MAY HENDRICKS</i>

793
01:09:34,271 --> 01:09:36,638
BEGAN TO BE DISTURBED

794
01:09:36,640 --> 01:09:39,474
<i>BY SCRATCHING SOUNDS</i>
<i>THAT CAME FROM THE BASEMENT..."</i>

795
01:09:39,476 --> 01:09:41,876
<i>( thunder crashes )</i>

796
01:09:43,846 --> 01:09:46,314
"...AND OBJECTS WERE
OFTEN FOUND TO BE MOVED

797
01:09:46,316 --> 01:09:48,583
<i>WITHOUT EXPLANATION.</i>

798
01:09:49,818 --> 01:09:51,853
SHE REPORTED TO HER HUSBAND

799
01:09:51,855 --> 01:09:54,689
THAT SHE'D FELT
REJECTED AND ALONE..."

800
01:10:02,198 --> 01:10:05,266
- ( moaning )
- <i>"...AND HAD BEEN INVADED</i>
<i>BY AN INVISIBLE ENTITY."</i>

801
01:10:06,235 --> 01:10:08,269
( creaks )

802
01:10:09,505 --> 01:10:11,339
<i>( Martha May whimpering )</i>

803
01:10:13,876 --> 01:10:15,977
( record scratching )

804
01:10:22,818 --> 01:10:24,419
( gasps, shuddering )

805
01:10:24,421 --> 01:10:26,254
<i>( wind gusting )</i>

806
01:10:27,523 --> 01:10:29,290
<i>( low growl )</i>

807
01:10:30,559 --> 01:10:32,493
"WHEN HER HUSBAND WAS
OUT OF TOWN,

808
01:10:32,495 --> 01:10:34,362
MARTHA MAY CLAIMED

809
01:10:34,364 --> 01:10:37,365
SHE WAS BEING ATTACKED
BY AN UNSEEN FORCE."

810
01:10:37,367 --> 01:10:39,701
( gasps )

811
01:10:39,703 --> 01:10:41,869
( screaming )

812
01:10:44,273 --> 01:10:45,907
<i>"...FOLLOWED OUT</i>
<i>TO THE GRANVILLE ESTATE,</i>

813
01:10:45,909 --> 01:10:49,611
- <i>WHERE AN EXORCISM</i>
<i>WAS ATTEMPTED."</i>
<i>- ( screaming )</i>

814
01:10:50,779 --> 01:10:53,381
S-U-E-D-O...

815
01:10:53,383 --> 01:10:55,416
"SHE KILLED HERSELF
WITH A BLADE

816
01:10:55,418 --> 01:10:57,885
AFTER A FAILED ATTEMPT
OF EXORCISM

817
01:10:57,887 --> 01:11:01,256
BY FATHER CALLAHAN
OF CORNERSTONE."

818
01:11:01,258 --> 01:11:02,423
NO!

819
01:11:04,293 --> 01:11:05,360
FATHER CALLAHAN.

820
01:11:10,399 --> 01:11:12,567
"MARTHA MAY HENDRICKS
IS SURVIVED

821
01:11:12,569 --> 01:11:16,337
BY HER HUSBAND
DEPUTY JED HENDRICKS."

822
01:11:18,641 --> 01:11:20,375
( exhales )

823
01:11:32,821 --> 01:11:35,590
<i>( bag dragging )</i>

824
01:11:35,592 --> 01:11:38,059
( humming )

825
01:11:50,873 --> 01:11:52,573
( humming stops )

826
01:12:32,915 --> 01:12:35,049
HOW COULD YOU
COVER THIS UP?

827
01:12:36,085 --> 01:12:38,086
HOW COULD YOU LIE
ABOUT THIS?

828
01:12:40,122 --> 01:12:43,091
YOU THINK
YOU KNOW A LOT, BUT...

829
01:12:44,793 --> 01:12:46,761
YOU DON'T KNOW
THE WHOLE STORY.

830
01:12:49,131 --> 01:12:51,499
I KNOW YOU'RE HIDING
BEHIND THIS.

831
01:12:56,105 --> 01:12:58,940
I WASN'T
ACTING UNDER GOD'S
AUTHORITY AND POWER

832
01:12:58,942 --> 01:13:00,942
WHEN I DID
THE DELIVERANCE.

833
01:13:01,910 --> 01:13:04,078
WAS I WRONG?

834
01:13:05,748 --> 01:13:07,482
ABSOLUTELY.

835
01:13:10,052 --> 01:13:12,019
WHAT IS IT THAT
YOU WANT FROM ME?

836
01:13:13,555 --> 01:13:15,423
MY WIFE

837
01:13:15,425 --> 01:13:17,392
NEEDS YOUR HELP.

838
01:13:18,160 --> 01:13:20,828
( chuckles )

839
01:13:20,830 --> 01:13:22,397
I CAN'T.

840
01:13:22,399 --> 01:13:24,465
LOOK, THIS-THIS--
THIS IS YOUR CHANCE

841
01:13:24,467 --> 01:13:26,033
FOR REDEMPTION
RIGHT HERE.

842
01:13:26,035 --> 01:13:27,935
NO ONE ELSE HAS SEEN
THIS BEFORE.

843
01:13:27,937 --> 01:13:29,871
I NEED YOUR HELP.
I'M BEGGIN' YOU.

844
01:13:34,743 --> 01:13:37,945
I SWORE I WOULDN'T
DO IT AGAIN.

845
01:13:37,947 --> 01:13:39,580
PLEASE.

846
01:13:46,422 --> 01:13:47,822
I CAN'T.

847
01:13:53,195 --> 01:13:55,463
I'M SORRY,
THERE'S NOTHING I CAN DO.

848
01:13:55,465 --> 01:13:59,066
YOU'RE A COWARD!
THAT'S ALL YOU ARE!
YOU'RE A FAKE!

849
01:14:27,763 --> 01:14:30,097
OH MY GOD.

850
01:14:30,099 --> 01:14:31,232
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?

851
01:14:31,234 --> 01:14:33,234
( demonic voice )
S-U-E-D-O-M-S-A.

852
01:14:33,236 --> 01:14:35,603
S-U-E-D-O-M-S-A.

853
01:14:38,207 --> 01:14:40,575
<i>( wind blowing )</i>

854
01:14:52,688 --> 01:14:55,256
- ( screams )
- I KNOW WHAT YOU DID.

855
01:14:55,258 --> 01:14:57,758
( gasps, moaning )

856
01:14:57,760 --> 01:15:01,496
YOUR WIFE IS
A WHORE IN HELL.

857
01:15:01,498 --> 01:15:02,230
( grunting )

858
01:15:02,232 --> 01:15:04,065
YOU TOOK EVERYTHING
FROM ME.

859
01:15:07,636 --> 01:15:09,637
Mike:
<i>RACHEL!</i>

860
01:15:11,507 --> 01:15:13,574
PUT THE KNIFE DOWN, OKAY?

861
01:15:14,243 --> 01:15:16,210
- RACHEL.
- RACHEL?

862
01:15:16,212 --> 01:15:19,247
OH, SHE'S NOT HERE
RIGHT NOW.

863
01:15:19,249 --> 01:15:20,848
( gate slams )

864
01:15:22,684 --> 01:15:24,252
WE CAN WORK
THIS OUT, OKAY?

865
01:15:25,153 --> 01:15:26,954
( grunts )

866
01:15:26,956 --> 01:15:30,157
( growling )
S-U-E-D-O-M-S-A.

867
01:15:30,159 --> 01:15:32,627
S-U-E-D-O-M-S-A.

868
01:15:32,629 --> 01:15:35,196
S-U-E-D-O--

869
01:15:36,198 --> 01:15:37,298
S-U-E-D-O-M-S-A.

870
01:15:37,300 --> 01:15:39,867
( shrieks )

871
01:15:39,869 --> 01:15:41,536
( yelps )

872
01:15:41,538 --> 01:15:43,237
( breathing heavily )

873
01:15:49,912 --> 01:15:52,613
I'VE WANDERED
THROUGH THE DESERT

874
01:15:52,615 --> 01:15:55,182
AND FOUND NO REST.

875
01:15:55,184 --> 01:15:57,919
"SWEPT AND GARNISHED,

876
01:15:57,921 --> 01:16:00,221
BUT STILL EMPTY."

877
01:16:00,223 --> 01:16:02,089
RACHEL!

878
01:16:05,160 --> 01:16:06,961
RACHEL!

879
01:16:08,630 --> 01:16:10,965
<i>( rattles, wind gusting )</i>

880
01:16:14,336 --> 01:16:16,337
Demonic Rachel:
<i>"GO PROCLAIM THE WORD.</i>

881
01:16:16,339 --> 01:16:18,239
<i>WHOEVER BELIEVES</i>
<i>WILL BE SAVED."</i>

882
01:16:18,241 --> 01:16:20,908
<i>IF YOU DON'T, YOU DIE.</i>
<i>YOUR BLOOD SPILLS.</i>

883
01:16:20,910 --> 01:16:23,744
<i>( laughter )</i>

884
01:16:23,746 --> 01:16:25,846
<i>"OH, IN MY NAME</i>

885
01:16:25,848 --> 01:16:28,015
<i>THEY WILL CAST OUT DEMONS,</i>

886
01:16:28,017 --> 01:16:30,284
<i>SPEAK IN TONGUES,</i>
<i>PICK UP SNAKES."</i>

887
01:16:30,286 --> 01:16:32,587
<i>AT THE RIGHT HAND</i>
<i>OF GOD I SIT.</i>

888
01:16:32,589 --> 01:16:35,856
ALL AUTHORITY ON EARTH
HAS BEEN GIVEN TO ME.

889
01:16:35,858 --> 01:16:38,793
- RACHEL!
- <i>( wailing )</i>

890
01:16:56,645 --> 01:16:58,646
RACHEL.

891
01:17:01,717 --> 01:17:03,751
IT'S ME.

892
01:17:03,753 --> 01:17:06,120
- IT'S MICHAEL.
- ( soft sobbing )

893
01:17:09,291 --> 01:17:10,658
HEY, SWEETIE,

894
01:17:10,660 --> 01:17:12,793
LISTEN,

895
01:17:12,795 --> 01:17:14,829
IT'S GONNA
BE OKAY, OKAY?

896
01:17:16,264 --> 01:17:18,332
- ( screams )
- HEY!

897
01:17:18,334 --> 01:17:21,335
- RACHEL!
- ( speaking Latin )

898
01:17:21,337 --> 01:17:23,638
- RACHEL, LISTEN TO ME!
- ( screams )

899
01:17:23,640 --> 01:17:26,641
- RACHEL, IT'S ME!
- ( screaming continues )

900
01:17:28,076 --> 01:17:30,344
IT'S ME!

901
01:17:31,279 --> 01:17:34,215
- RACHEL!
- "I SAW SATAN FALL

902
01:17:34,217 --> 01:17:36,350
<i>LIKE LIGHTNING</i>
<i>FROM HEAVEN.</i>

903
01:17:36,352 --> 01:17:38,252
BEHOLD,

904
01:17:38,254 --> 01:17:41,022
I HAVE GIVEN YOU AUTHORITY
TO TREAD ON SERPENTS."

905
01:17:43,959 --> 01:17:45,426
RACHEL!

906
01:17:45,428 --> 01:17:46,961
( shouts )

907
01:17:53,669 --> 01:17:55,870
